 examples of\nrational relations for which such logics are decidable even without syntactic\nrestrictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2013 16:15:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Jul 2013 21:55:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-14"}
